nodes.text: Search and Rescue Squad 204 was a Republic squad posted on Taris and commanded by Elara Dorne. Members of the squad included Corporal Tabber, Ensign Vise, Ensign Marko, Corporal Goran and Ensign Cav. Elara Dorne led the squad to rescue Ensign Tane and other captive Republic soldiers from the Fallenspire Stronghold.
